The paper discusses the design and implementation of a visual search system for real-time image retrieval on an e-commerce platform. This involves handling large amounts of data and frequent updates, which suggests that the paper could belong to the Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Computer Vision (cs.CV), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), Database (cs.DB), or Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories.
